  "prompt": "Where can I get very professional fire inspection service in Sydney?",
  "response": "In Sydney, there are several companies that offer professional fire inspection services. Here are a few options to consider:\n\n1. **Fire Protection Association Australia (FPA Australia)** - They can provide you with a list of accredited fire inspectors and related services. Their website has resources and links to certified professionals.\n\n2. **Fire Safety Australia** - They offer comprehensive fire safety services, including inspections, compliance audits, and maintenance. \n\n3. **National Fire Safety** - They provide a range of fire safety services, including inspections and assessments, ensuring compliance with Australian standards.\n\n4. **PyroShield** - Specializing in fire safety systems and inspections, they can help ensure your premises meet all fire safety regulations.\n\n5. **Hastings Fire Services** - They offer fire safety compliance services including inspections, training, and equipment maintenance.\n\nMake sure to check reviews and verify their credentials before hiring any service. It\u2019s also a good idea to get quotes from a few companies to compare services and pricing.",
